    {
      "locale": "zhCN",
      "text": "“埃拉娜，我们差不多该回去和其他人汇合了。”",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-02T08:03:33.3231477Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-02T08:03:33.3231478Z",
      "original_text": "\"I suppose, Elana, we ought to return to the others.\"",
      "traits": [
        {
