        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Nous devrions sans doute rejoindre les autres, Elana. »",
      "modification_date": "2026-04-03T08:25:52.6250722Z",
      "translated_from": "enGB",
      "translation_date": "2026-04-03T08:25:52.6250724Z",
      "original_text": "\"I suppose, Elana, we ought to return to the others.\"",
